items.name: PyWhiteBox
items.description: PyWhiteBox is a web-based Python testing tool that allows users to easily test their code. By simply pasting or entering the code into an input field, users can select different testing modes (Basic Path Testing, Path Coverage Testing, Large Model Testing) to automatically generate corresponding test flowcharts and detailed test cases.
